<div class="panel panel-default" id="login">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed ad illum redeo. Efficiens dici potest. Satis est ad
      hoc responsum. Ita prorsus, inquam; </p>

    <p>Quid iudicant sensus? Duo Reges: constructio interrete. Sed residamus, inquit, si placet. Praeclare hoc
      quidem. </p>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-body">
    <%= bootstrap_form_tag url: sessions_path do |f| %>

        <%= f.text_field :identity %>
        <%= f.password_field :password %>

        <%= f.submit t('login') %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="panel-footer">
    <div class="pull-left"><%= link_to t('signup'), signup_path, class: 'pull-left' %></div>
    <div class="pull-right"><%= link_to t('password.reset'), new_password_reset_path %></div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
</div>



